Citation.sTitle: Experimental Binary VLE Data of Morpholine with 1-Butanol and 3-Methyl-1-butanol Systems
Citation.sAbstract: New vapour liquid equilibrium (VLE) PTx data for two binary mixtures morpholine with 1-butanol and morpholine with 3- methyl-1-butanol under 13 conditions have been measured through Sweitoslawski type ebulliometer. Each set of experimental PTx data has been correlated by five activity coefficient models using GN optimization procedure, Wilson single parameter, Wilson single-set data treatment and two versions of the UNIFAC method. Comparisons also made between available literature values and published data with present experimental vapour liquid equilibrium PTx data. The azeotropic points have been determined using the method of Mixon et al.
